---
import HokkaidoScene from './HokkaidoScene.astro';
import { HOK_CITIES } from '../lib/cities';
---

<section class="hk-hero">
  <div class="hk-hero-art">
    <HokkaidoScene />
  </div>
  <div class="hk-hero-inner">
    <div class="hk-eyebrow fp-mono">hokkaido.fujioha.com · 旅のガイド</div>
    <h1 class="hk-title fp-jp">北海道の<br />歩き方</h1>
    <p class="hk-title-en fp-en">Hokkaido, on foot — by someone who lives here.</p>
    <p class="hk-lede">
      <span class="fp-jp"
        >観光ガイドには載らない、地元の人の朝の回り方。住んでいる人間が、実際に歩く順番で書いています。</span
      >
      <span class="fp-en fp-mute"
        >A travel guide written from the inside — the routes, the hours, and the
        small detours a local actually takes.</span
      >
    </p>
    <div class="hk-hero-meta">
      <span class="hk-chip fp-mono">{HOK_CITIES.length} 都市 · cities</span>
      <span class="hk-chip fp-mono">14 記事 · guides</span>
      <span class="hk-chip fp-mono">今週更新 · updated this week</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
